  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "c8437183-9818-473d-a566-55d14d538af8"],
 " for details."
}], "Notes",
 CellID->321089908,ExpressionUUID->"3195f2a8-edce-4969-bac0-7ab0aa084bc1"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "It randomly generates  a sequence of random \"Bravyi circuits\" (i.e., \
quantum circuits of fermionic Gaussian gates or measurement of fermion modes) \
 ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  StyleBox["circuits", "TI"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "e7e0e261-763b-4fd8-8db3-af93ac94f769"],
 ": ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   StyleBox["circuits", "TI"], "=", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["qc", "TI"], 
      StyleBox["1", "TR"]], ",", 
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["qc", "TI"], 
      StyleBox["2", "TR"]], ",", 
     StyleBox["\[Ellipsis]", "TR"]}], "}"}]}]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "7b9183e4-5c1b-4d33-b2c4-5fead53e2c00"],
 " , simulates them, and return a list of resulting quantum states ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   StyleBox["data", "TI"], "=", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["set", "TI"], 
      StyleBox["1", "TR"]], ",", 
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["set", "TI"], 
      StyleBox["2", "TR"]], ",", 
     StyleBox["\[Ellipsis]", "TR"]}], "}"}]}]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "48fcac40-97b7-44f9-8910-8a1477e00b9b"],
 ". The latter contains subsets of trajectories, each subset ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["set", "TI"], 
    StyleBox["i", "TI"]], "=", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["trj", "TI"], 
      StyleBox[
       RowBox[{
        StyleBox["i", "TI"], 
        StyleBox["1", "TR"]}],
       ZeroWidthTimes->True]], ",", 
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["trj", "TI"], 
      StyleBox[
       RowBox[{
        StyleBox["i", "TI"], 
        StyleBox["2", "TR"]}],
       ZeroWidthTimes->True]], ",", 
     StyleBox["\[Ellipsis]", "TR"]}], "}"}]}]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "074d7a43-4323-4e73-bbb0-840de38f9a11"],
 " collects the trajectories from quantum circuit ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox[
   StyleBox["qc", "TI"], 
   StyleBox["i", "TI"]]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "54fbe3ea-e28a-41af-b015-50a23c3b0212"],
 ". Each quantum trajectory ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["trj", "TI"], 
    StyleBox["ij", "TI"]], "=", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["ws", "TI"], 
      StyleBox["ij1", "TI"]], ",", 
     SubscriptBox[
      StyleBox["ws", "TI"], 
      StyleBox["ij2", "TI"]], ",", 
     StyleBox["\[Ellipsis]", "TR"]}], "}"}]}]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "aab4b741-772b-41dd-ab83-6a40cfb98164"],
 " is a sequence of quantum states ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox[
   StyleBox["ws", "TI"], 
   StyleBox["ijt", "TI"]]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "df27ecfa-f375-4271-94d4-81b7be69e63a"],
 ", which are in the ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  TemplateBox[{
    Cell[
     TextData["BravyiState"]], "paclet:QuantumMob/Q3/ref/BravyiState", 
    "QuantumMob Package Symbol"},
   "PackageLink",
   BaseStyle->"InlineFormula"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
  "020b569f-ca36-445e-adef-77c7f7bf465a"],
 " object. "
}], "Notes",
 CellID->10304835,ExpressionUUID->"018348b6-1f8e-4b9c-9685-0b65e42677c4"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "It returns a pair ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{"{", 
